    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, optimized by six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Mechanically, it is flawless: rod bearings were replaced proactively, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a fresh clutch and a tight limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its original factory luster with no signs of paint correction or panel misalignment. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters show no wear, reflecting its meticulously maintained history. Zero leaks, zero codes, and a comprehensive service dossier included.",
